The National Center for State Courts, a non-profit organization produced this to scare students away from filesharing. This is meant to be distributed to middle and high schools. The story is riddled with inaccurate information about the legal system, which makes it even better -- make a scavenger hunt of it!

Keep an eye on the news, since we&amp;#039;ll probably find out sooner or later who funds this group.

